&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain QA/QC manuals, inspection checklists, and standard operating procedures (SOPs) for all field and reporting functions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish quality metrics, KPIs, and reporting cadences to drive continuous improvement across all business lines&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead root cause analysis (RCA) and corrective action processes for quality escapes, recurring deficiencies, and customer-reported issues&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
